THE REPOSITORY PROVIDES THE FORM OF THE METRIC FUNCTIONS AND OF 
AUXILIARY FIELDS (AS SCALAR) FOR BLACK HOLE SOLUTIONS IN 
MODIFIED THEORIES OF GRAVIY. THE GEODESIC STRUCTURE FOR 
MASSIVE/MASSLESS PARTICLES IS ALSO PROVIDED.

DEPENDING ON THE THEROY, QUANTITIES ARE GIVEN IN DIFFERENT 
FUNCTIONAL FORMS, E.G. AS SMALL SPIN EXPANSION OF THE BH SPIN AND 
OF THE THEORY COUPLING PARAMENTER (more details in main.nb)

THEORY COVERED

- EINSTEIN DILATON GAUSS BONNET GRAVITY 
- DYNAMICAL CHERN SIMONS GRAVITY
- EFFECTIVE FIELD THEORY EXTENSSION OF GENERAL RELATIVITY

